## SSRM IMPLEMENTATION MAPPING: itemLibrary, prod_tracking, licensing_tracking

### FRONTEND GRIDOPTIONS CONFIGURATION

**itemLibrary** (designflow-frontend/src/app/pages/itemLibrary/itemLibrary.component.ts:226-285):
